code: @Test public void sendIn() throws Exception {     result.expectedMessageCount(1).     template.sendBody("direct:listObjects", ExchangePattern.InOnly, "").     assertMockEndpointsSatisfied().     assertResultExchange(result.getExchanges().get(0)). }

private void assertResultExchange(Exchange resultExchange) {     ObjectListing list = resultExchange.getIn().getBody(ObjectListing.class).     assertEquals(1, list.getObjectSummaries().size()).     assertEquals("Myfile", list.getObjectSummaries().get(0).getKey()).     assertEquals("test", list.getObjectSummaries().get(0).getBucketName()). }

@Override protected JndiRegistry createRegistry() throws Exception {     JndiRegistry registry = super.createRegistry().     client = new AmazonS3ClientMock().     registry.bind("amazonS3Client", client).     return registry. }
